OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,FA Somerset man who became stranded in
OL,7,FGreece after falling ill on holiday
OL,8,Fhas died from septic shock, his family
OL,9,Fsay.
OL,11,FAlan Kirby, 67, from Marston Magna was
OL,12,Fenjoying a family trip to Zante when
OL,13,Fhe began experiencing a pain in his
OL,14,Fside.
OL,16,FMedics in Athens subsequently
OL,17,Fdiagnosed him with pneumonia and
OL,18,Fsuspected lung cancer. His family say
OL,19,Fthere was no indication Mr Kirby was
OL,20,Fseriously unwell before they travelled.
