OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,FHowever, he'd been diagnosed with a
OL,7,Fbenign lung tumour the previous year -
OL,8,Fa condition that required no active
OL,9,Ftreatment and seemed to have no impact
OL,10,Fon his daily life.
OL,12,FTo Alan and his family, the inactive
OL,13,Ftumour appeared irrelevant to their
OL,14,Fholiday plans and so they did not
OL,15,Fdeclare it when purchasing travel
OL,16,Finsurance.
