OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,FTheir insurers Allianz, however, said
OL,7,Fthis omission was grounds to deny
OL,8,Fcoverage entirely, regardless of
OL,9,Fwhether the undisclosed condition was
OL,10,Fdirectly related to his current crisis.
OL,12,FIn a statement on 3 August, Allianz
OL,13,Fexplained: "Our sympathies are with Mr
OL,14,FKirby and his family during his
OL,15,Frecovery.
OL,17,F"In common with other travel insurers,
OL,18,Fwe ask customers to adhere to policy
OL,19,Fterms, including disclosure of any pre-
OL,20,Fexisting medical conditions for anyone
OL,21,Fcovered under the policy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
