OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, a pre-existing medical
OL,7,Fcondition was not disclosed to us, so
OL,8,Fwe are declining the claim. We acted
OL,9,Fin good faith and covered the costs of
OL,10,FMr Kirby until the pre-existing
OL,11,Fmedical condition was established."
OL,13,FMr Kirby was then stranded in Greece
OL,14,Fand, legally, the only way he could
OL,15,Ffly home to the NHS would have been on
OL,16,Fa medical flight with a specialist
OL,17,Fnurse, at a cost of #30,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
