OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,FOn 3 August, ITV News West Country
OL,7,Freported that Mr Kirby's family were
OL,8,Ffundraising online to be able to bring
OL,9,Fhim home.
OL,11,FSince then, they have used the page to
OL,12,Fupdate friends, family and donors on
OL,13,Fhis condition.
OL,15,FBy 8 August, Mr Kirby was receiving
OL,16,Foxygen and in a medically-induced coma.
OL,18,FHis daughter Liza Whitemore was able
OL,19,Fto speak to his nurses who said that
OL,20,Fanother mass had been found, and he
OL,21,Fwas on antibiotics for an infection.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
