OL,3,CMan stranded in Greece after falling
OL,4,Cill died from septic shock, family say
OL,6,FBy 22 August, Ms Whitemore wrote, the
OL,7,Fmedics were considering a tracheostomy
OL,8,F- inserting a tube directly into her
OL,9,Ffather's windpipe - as they believed
OL,10,Fthe ventilation tubes in his mouth may
OL,11,Fbe causing the infection.
OL,13,FThree days later she wrote that he was
OL,14,Fsuffering from multi-organ failure and
OL,15,Fseptic shock. He died overnight on
OL,16,FTuesday 26 August.
OL,18,FHis family say they're now planning to
OL,19,Ffly out to Athens and to use the money
OL,20,Fdonated to their crowdfunding page for
OL,21,FMr Kirby's cremation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
